    "body" : "<p>You should add</p>\n<pre><code>        &lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>to your code.</p>\n<p>Besides, if you want to see the changes without clicking reload or pressing<br />\n<strong>Ctrl + R</strong> to refresh the page, then add the <em>LiveReload</em> extension to your browser.</p>\n<p>For Firefox:<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/livereload-web-extension/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/livereload-web-extension/</a></p>\n<p>After you have added it to your browser, right-click and choose <strong>“Pin to toolbar”</strong>.<br />\nAt the top right, you should see an icon; click on it.<br />\nWhen it turns blue, it means it’s activated, and you can see changes without manually reloading the page.</p>\n"
